      "author": "MediaVoice (Ali Ahmed Brohi)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hi everyone, I am fairly new to <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a>.</p>\n<p>I am having an issue with charts. The figures are not shown as I have aligned the items in Main table.<br />\nChart:<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/3/3fb70321c74d23f8d67cacf2513f8e26373ca465.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/3/3fb70321c74d23f8d67cacf2513f8e26373ca465_2_690x214.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"214\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1470×456 17.8 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><br />\nMain Table:<br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/9/93ea7446a17eadcc39bca6177a96124ad2f8a66a.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/9/93ea7446a17eadcc39bca6177a96124ad2f8a66a_2_690x496.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"496\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">753×542 17.9 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Thank you!</p>"
