      "author": "TMNXT-Dev (Ilja Zweigert)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hey <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/mediavoice\">@MediaVoice</a> ,</p>\n<p>quick walkthrough:</p>\n<p><strong>Create a “Date” column:</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/f/f4dcabd4fd64536d7f763d9b873f753e599e215b.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"331\" height=\"383\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Set months:</strong></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/5/533173846a4738db1b2e1a1d2026dc13d6fc5c7e.png\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/5/533173846a4738db1b2e1a1d2026dc13d6fc5c7e.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"545\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">567×520 18.6 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p><strong>Sort by Date:</strong></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/d/dbe079b9bc3106d22fc7974ee3cf3de15a5c2df2.png\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/d/dbe079b9bc3106d22fc7974ee3cf3de15a5c2df2_2_293x500.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"293\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">382×651 13.1 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p><strong>There you go:</strong></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/1/17f41b2f8d2c79048bb657e97c90b66ff5083eb8.png\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/1/17f41b2f8d2c79048bb657e97c90b66ff5083eb8_2_690x329.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"329\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">845×403 14.5 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Greetings</p>"
