      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hi,<br />\nI am having the same issue. My main board looks like this:<br />\n2023 Budget   LinkedCol    Formula Col    2023 Actual    2022     2021     2020     2019<br />\nRevenues                                                                                10                    500      200      100        50</p>\n<p>Expenses                                                                                 -5                   -100    -50        -20      -10</p>\n<p>The Chart displays the Net Income (Revenues - Expenses) correctly.</p>\n<p>However, the chart shows the years in a random order:</p>\n<p>2023 Actual     2018    2023 Budget    2022    2017    2021    2020    2019</p>\n<p>I don’t understand the recommendation to change my number columns to “date” columns.  I need to input revenues and expenses…not dates</p>"
